input: This web page is about a small business that sells crafts.
output: This web page is about a small business, Crafts by Cindy, that specializes in hand-crafted items. Customers can find a selection of ceramic, woodwork, and fabric items, all created with care by Cindy. Cindy also offers custom orders to meet customers’ individual needs. All orders are shipped promptly and with detailed instructions on how the crafted items should be handled. Crafts by Cindy offers a perfect way to give one-of-a-kind gifts or decorate your home with unique items.
